        </p>

        <form
          class="c-form"
          method="get">
          <div class="c-message c-message--danger">
            <p>
              Bon ... nous avons un sérieux problème de nature relativement
              globale.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="c-formsection">
            <div class="c-formfield">
              <div>
                <label
                  class="c-formfield__label"
                  for="name">
                  Nom
                  <span class="c-formfield__required">*</span>
                </label>
                <div class="c-formfield__help">
                  <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                    Nobis, officia esse eveniet doloribus natus beatae unde,
                    perferendis culpa error.
                  </p>
